Known issues:
  - If the MLX90393 is in burst mode then reading often fails.
    Please do NOT report this issue unless you can help me with
    insights why this happens. Even better: provide a pull request
    with a fix.

  - Register access to MLX90393 does not work while in burst mode.
    This is how the chip operates and not a bug of the debug helper.
    From the point of view of the debug helper this is a feature.